1
00:00:00,610 --> 00:00:02,240
Sigh.

2
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:04,840
Is something wrong?

3
00:00:05,240 --> 00:00:06,090
Actually...

4
00:00:06,090 --> 00:00:08,880
I got into a fight with Mizuki yesterday.

5
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:11,220
With Mizuki? But she's so sweet.

6
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,350
Yeah.

7
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:15,180
How did that happen?

8
00:00:15,310 --> 00:00:17,640
It was my fault.

9
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:20,480
I always take her kindness for granted.

10
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:24,360
Well, you've always needed looking after.

11
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:25,650
Exactly.

12
00:00:25,650 --> 00:00:30,950
I thought I grew up
once I got a job.

13
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:36,200
But even at work,
I rely on Kamiki-san to get by.

14
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:39,040
I'm doing everything I can
just to keep up.

15
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:42,210
I wanted to make things
easier for you guys.

16
00:00:43,420 --> 00:00:47,800
But I'm still acting like a kid.

17
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:53,800
Mizuki is so much more mature than me.

18
00:00:57,350 --> 00:00:59,390
You dummy, you understand perfectly.

19
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:01,140
Huh?

20
00:01:01,140 --> 00:01:04,270
Now that you get it,
go apologize to her.

21
00:01:04,270 --> 00:01:05,270
Huh? Right now?

22
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:06,070
Yes, right now.

23
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:08,690
Apologizing immediately
is a salesman's golden rule.

24
00:01:08,690 --> 00:01:10,150
But what about work?

25
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:12,240
I'll explain it to the manager.

26
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,240
Go on.

27
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,580
Okay. Thank you.
